:::Orion/Sideswipe:::

::Orion was hit by Blowpipe's shots and a few of Perceptor's shots.  As the 
energy net from Surgital started coming down, Orion looked to Sideswipe::
Orion: Watch out!
::He pushes Sideswipe aside and falls to the ground away from the net.  As 
Cuttrhoat starts trying to bite at him, Orion laughs::
Orion: Please.
::He fired 1 missle at Cutthroat and 1 at Triggerhappy::
~~~~~
::Sideswipe gets up from the ground and gives Orion thumbs up::
Sideswipe: Thanks buddy!
::He gets hit by Perceptor's shots. He fired 2 missles at Surgital and 25 
rifle shots at Perceptor::
